::'''Leonard:''' Mmm? Are you encountering any problems? Just hit up the front desk down the corridor that way... Ah! What's this error doing here!?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you Leonard?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_800090105-->
